dct_title_s: Park Ridge, Bergen County, New Jersey : including Montvale (Sheet 1)
dct_description_sm: "November 1924." Includes location map, streets and specials index, key and text. "1971." Historic Maps has sheets 1-5, showing Park Ridge; sheets 6-7, showing Montvale, foldered separately.
dct_publisher_sm: New York : Sanborn Map Company, 1924, c1925.
